{"adult":false,"also_known_as":["Fengyi Zhang","张丰毅","Zhang Feng-Yi","Zhang fengyi"],"biography":"张丰毅，1956年9月1日生于湖南省长沙市，1982年毕业于北京电影学院，中国电影表演艺术协会副会长、中国电影协会理事。\n\n1981年，主演电影《骆驼祥子》，1990年，凭借《龙年警官》获得第3届中国电影表演协会优秀男演员奖。1993年与张国荣、巩俐主演的电影《霸王别姬》获得戛纳国际电影节金棕榈奖。1996年凭借《和平年代》夺得飞天奖优秀男演员奖；2005年，凭借《历史的天空》再次夺得第25届全国电视剧飞天奖优秀男演员。2009年，出演吴宇森导演的电影《赤壁》，饰演曹操。\n\n2015年1月19日，加盟2015年央视羊年春晚，搭档段奕宏、朱亚文演唱歌曲《中华好儿孙》。2015年5月，参加湖南卫视国防教育特别节目《真正男子汉》录制。2017年3月，主演的当代反腐电视剧《人民的名义》播出。","birthday":"1956-09-01","id":65277,"imdb_id":"nm0955342","name":"Zhang Fengyi","place_of_birth":"Changsha, Hunan, China","popularity":1.054,"profile_path":"/l3PtQzEU84l7B9XA6SitAGIIJqH.jpg","credits":{"cast":[{"id":67080,"title":"杀人者唐斩","character":"Tang Zhan / Tang Bao Jia","original_title":"Sha ren zhe Tang Zhan","poster_path":"/kC6sf8I1tje5LmKieP5s5uZkjI2.jpg","release_date":"1993-09-23","adult":false},{"id":10387,"title":"荆轲刺秦王","character":"Jing Ke","original_title":"荊軻刺秦王","poster_path":"/z0ishYoY4CqSMk6POHWf75Dq1BO.jpg","release_date":"1998-10-08","adult":false},{"id":263171,"title":"日光峽谷","character":"","original_title":"日光峽谷","release_date":"1996-05-30","adult":false},{"id":320158,"title":"京都球侠","character":"Zhou Tian","original_title":"Jing du qiu xia","poster_path":"/kQyBDzDzzK5DMxhKVrYHTsXb8Yl.jpg","release_date":"1987-01-01","adult":false},{"id":440334,"title":"青春无悔","character":"","original_title":"青春无悔","release_date":"1991-01-01","adult":false},{"id":495954,"title":"檔案X殺人犯","character":"Chief Lok Bin","original_title":"檔案X殺人犯","poster_path":"/pJ7MZ4o4nNgQrLzjx03qB93ntHd.jpg","release_date":"1997-10-30","adult":false},{"id":572272,"title":"跟我走一回","character":"Ma Boon Shing","original_title":"跟我走一回","release_date":"1995-10-26","adult":false},{"id":334519,"title":"Xin bao chou","character":"","original_title":"Xin bao chou","release_date":"1994-01-01","adult":false},{"id":667059,"title":"龙年警官","character":"傅冬","original_title":"龙年警官","poster_path":"/yjfEUeOLM7vGq5kP9z9uXFCaLAM.jpg","release_date":"1990-01-01","a